.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-HTLC-LIST" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-htlc-list \- list pending HTLCs across all channels
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-htlc-list
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns all in-flight HTLCs across every channel as a JSON array.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{channel_id, direction, amount_msat, expiry, payment_hash}]
.fi
Returns an empty array when the daemon is not reachable or there are
no pending HTLCs.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-list (1),
.BR lightning-node-health (1)
